COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 500, L.D. 1211
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment strikes the bill and changes the title. The amendment exempts short-
33 term grants of a privilege to use sports and recreational equipment, based on the length of
44 the grant, the value of the property and where the equipment is used.
